To Whom It May Concern,

I am hereby requesting access pursuant to Article 15 of the GDPR. Please confirm whether or not you are processing personal data concerning me (as specified in Art. 15(1) GDPR).

In case you are, I request you to provide me with the following information pursuant to Art. 15(1) GDPR:
1. All personal data concerning me that you have stored;
2. The purposes of the processing;
3. The categories of personal data concerned;
4. The recipients to whom my data has been disclosed;
5. The envisaged storage period;
6. Information about the source of the data.

If you have transferred my personal data to a third country or an international organisation, I request to be informed about the appropriate safeguards according to Art. 46 GDPR.

[FILL IN: Your identification data, e.g. full name, date of birth, address, email address]

Please respond within one month as required by Art. 12(3) GDPR.

Sincerely,
[FILL IN: Your name]
